<script lang="ts">let{data}=$props();</script><svelte:head><title>读者账号｜暮色工作台</title></svelte:head><header class="studio-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">READERS</p><h1>读者账号</h1><p>查看已注册用户和最近登录时间，可停用异常账号。</p></div></header><section class="studio-panel user-table"><header><span>用户</span><span>邮箱</span><span>注册与登录</span><span>状态</span></header>{#each data.users as user}<article><div><span class="user-avatar">{user.username.slice(0,1)}</span><b>{user.username}</b></div><span>{user.email}</span><small>注册 {new Date(user.createdAt).toLocaleDateString('zh-CN')}<br/>登录 {user.lastLoginAt?new Date(user.lastLoginAt).toLocaleDateString('zh-CN'):'—'}</small><form method="POST" action="?/toggle"><input type="hidden" name="id" value={user.id}/><input type="hidden" name="status" value={user.status}/><button class:danger={user.status==='active'}>{user.status==='active'?'停用':'恢复'}</button></form></article>{:else}<div class="empty">还没有注册用户。</div>{/each}</section>
